item.title: Prayer bpn13466 in Chichewa
item.description: O Ambuye Mulungu Wanga! Thandizani wokondedwa Anu kukhala wolimba mâ€™chikhulupiliro chanu, kuyenda munjira Zanu, ndikukhala wochilimika mu ntchito Yanu. Apatseni chisomo Chanu kuti athe kulimbana ndi zilakolako zawo, kutsata kuwala kwa chitsogozo chauzimu. Inu Ndinu Wamphamvu, Wachisomo, Wodzidalira Nokha, Wopereka Madalitso, Wachikondi, Wamkulu, Wachaulere Chonse. (Source category: KULIMBIKIRA) (Bahaiprayers.net ID: 13466)
